'''Yibal''' is the largest [[oilfield]] in [[Oman]]. It began production in 1968, and at its peak had a production of nearly {{Convert|250000|oilbbl/d|m3/d}}. In recent years, it has begun to decline, and in 2005 produces about {{Convert|88000|oilbbl/d|m3/d}}. The Yibal oil field is operated primarily by [[Petroleum Development Oman]].
